Strata-management company:A strata-management company is a company that manages and maintains common property in a strata scheme, such as apartment buildings or townhouses.
Low-powered air conditioner:A low-powered air conditioner is a type of air conditioner that has a lower cooling capacity and energy consumption compared to high-powered models.
High-powered air conditioner:A high-powered air conditioner is a type of air conditioner that has a higher cooling capacity and energy consumption compared to low-powered models.
